📌 Description

This project is a presentation/module designed to educate users about phishing attacks and how to stay safe online.

🎯 Objectives
Explain phishing attacks
Identify phishing emails and fake websites
Understand social engineering tactics
Provide safety tips and best practices
📚 Content Includes
Phishing concepts and types
Real-world examples
Recognition techniques
Prevention tips
Interactive quizzes
🛡️ Outcome

Users will learn how to detect phishing attempts and protect their personal information.
